property_description: Experience elevated island living in this stunning penthouse level residence at Ae‘o with extra tall 10 foot ceilings, in one of Honolulu’s most sought-after luxury condominiums in the heart of Ward Village. #PH3907 also comes with storage, making it the perfect home or investment opportunity. As you step inside, you’re greeted by floor-to-ceiling windows that frame sweeping Kaka’ako city, ocean, and mountain views, flooding the space with natural light. The open layout maximizes space & flow, featuring a gourmet kitchen with sleek cabinetry, quartz countertops, and Bosch appliances. The spacious bedroom provides a serene retreat with a walk in closet, while the spa-like bathroom boasts contemporary design. Living at Ae‘o means access to resort-style amenities, including a stunning rooftop terrace, two pools, fitness center, sauna, private movie theater, karaoke room, guest suites, and multiple entertainment areas. Plus, enjoy the convenience of direct access to Whole Foods Market downstairs and being just steps from Ward Village’s premier shopping, dining, and entertainment. Don’t miss your chance to own a luxury home in the heart of Honolulu. Schedule your showing today!

265 Uki Uki Loop at Mahana Estates is a premier 0.744-acre parcel that captures the very best of Kapalua’s breathtaking natural beauty and elevated lifestyle. Gently sloping and backing directly onto the 6th hole of the world-famous Plantation Course, this homesite commands unobstructed ocean views across Kapalua Bay to Molokini, while the West Maui Mountains provide a dramatic, verdant backdrop. Experience radiant sunrises over the mountains and unforgettable sunsets over the Pacific. This shovel-ready lot includes completed building plans for a 3,716-square-foot custom estate plus 1,203 square feet of covered lanai space, thoughtfully designed for seamless indoor-outdoor living. The layout features 4 bedrooms, 4.5 bathrooms, a dedicated office, and a separate guest wing with two bedrooms, two bathrooms, and a lock-off option. The outdoor design includes a 27.6' x 18' swimming pool, a separate elevated spa, and a dedicated Baja shelf for sun lounging. A 538-square-foot garage completes the plan. Mahana Estates is a gated, low-density community offering private water, underground utilities, completed infrastructure, and protective height restrictions to preserve view corridors. The lot's gentle topography supports efficient construction and optimal home placement. Just minutes from the world-class amenities of Kapalua Resort, including the Spa Montage, Kapalua Bay and Plantation Golf Courses, scenic hiking trails, and the golden sands of Flemings Beach, Lot 15 offers a rare opportunity to create a legacy estate in one of Maui’s most prestigious resort communities.

Private 2-Acre Estate on Former Mac Nut Orchard | Permitted Custom Home + Expansion Opportunity Permitted two-story, custom-designed home nestled in the upper Puna rainforest of Fern Acres, located at the beginning of a paved road just 8 miles from Keaʻau and approximately 15 miles from Hilo and Volcano. Situated on a private 2-acre parcel within a former macadamia nut orchard, this property offers peaceful island living with future potential. The upper level features vaulted beam ceilings, bamboo flooring, and an open-concept living, kitchen, and dining area. Numerous sliding glass doors and windows create the feeling of a luxury treehouse. The primary bedroom and bath are also upstairs, along with approximately 780 sq ft of wrap-around deck space extending from the primary lanai to the kitchen and dining lanai. Wake to birdsong, enjoy sunrise from the front lanai, and on clear days take in views of Mauna Kea and Mauna Loa. The lower level includes two additional bedrooms, a playroom or office, and a newly refinished bathroom with new tile, tub, sink, and cabinet. Recent upgrades include new interior and exterior paint, stove, dishwasher, and 22 mil LifeProof vinyl plank flooring downstairs. Two adjacent 2-acre parcels are also available. Buyer of the home receives first right of refusal on both. Home parcel eligible for financing; vacant land available via cash purchase You can view drone footage of the home by clicking on the link https://youtube.com/shorts/G1Bk83sw8GY
